{"tid":1026701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛鵝山上遇野豬　青年疑掉垃圾挑釁　網民斥無知","createTime":"2019-02-18T10:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T12:30:01.000Z","uid":225464,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc316275768b0ab0ee2870e57d75183068436e9","tid":1026701,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>飛鵝山上遇野豬 青年疑掉垃圾挑釁 網民斥無知</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190218/bkn-20190218163526479-0218_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190218%2Fbkn-20190218163526479-0218_00822_001.html&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c6d3f753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190218/bkn-20190218163526479-0218_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190218/photo/bkn-20190218163526479-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190218170215\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190218163526479-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190218170215&h=b1edded7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n各有各生活唔得咩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n野豬在山上生活，也不能得片刻寧靜嗎？近日在飛鵝山上有一群青年遇上落單的野豬，竟嬉皮笑臉地將一袋疑似垃圾丟向牠，網民紛斥無知！<br />\n<br />\n香港野豬關注組上周五（15日）在其Facebook專頁分享片段，指當日下午約6時，約10名手持攝影器材的男女在飛鵝山道遇上野豬，當時青年聚在一邊，與野豬相隔一條馬路。<br />\n<br />\n當野豬徐徐走向青年時，其中一名男子突然從地上拾起紅色膠袋拋向野豬。袋中雜物四散飄落，嚇得野豬連退數步。他們大着膽子走近野豬，有人又不斷將散落的垃圾踢向牠。<br />\n<br />\n香港野豬關注組呼籲，若市民在山上遇到野豬或其他野生動物，「請保持冷靜，不要做出驚慌舉動，更不要餵食，尊重野外生態」。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛斥責青年過分︰「搞到一地垃圾，仲咁開心，一啲公德都冇」、「我只見到人類嘅無知及對動物嘅傷害性」、「假如野豬被嚇親反擊，野豬又會被形容成兇惡動物被趕絕」、「如果佢哋畀野豬攻擊，我覺得一啲都唔可憐」。"},{"pid":"db8ec0daebfb8287250e1cec923c37b89771b71f","tid":1026701,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28adf40db62dcf7eb40bdcf6142f12a1d26db16","tid":1026701,"uid":25858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"野豬發惡佢地就知死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb0cffcbb959c4710c2a55cac840d655aa0aedb","tid":1026701,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係唔嚇死 野豬仲癲撚過野狗  又撞又咬 又記仇 <br />\n班仆街今次真係算好彩 比人公審下算係咁 之後記得去還神"},{"pid":"9378bd0a1bc921de2e164ce78c26dd41eeff00f5","tid":1026701,"uid":35930,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"個死𡃁仔係咪未玩過aoe"},{"pid":"cb6398d1ff90450c5d602a78583845c51c721b34","tid":1026701,"uid":47374,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"以前要7個成年人拎晒弓箭先搞掂到一隻野豬<br />\n仲要間唔中死1個，乜而家啲人咁勇敢"},{"pid":"9b0e3c121c0039503e6d365db22651867a49d6b5","tid":1026701,"uid":33176,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"呢隻港豬嚟㗎<br />\n俾人恰到上心口都唔會反抗㗎"},{"pid":"8f2b18cf51fdff283043654dcb132477e6c45106","tid":1026701,"uid":199613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9378bd0a1bc921de2e164ce78c26dd41eeff00f5","tid":1026701,"uid":35930,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:04:47.000Z","msg":"個死𡃁仔係咪未玩過aoe"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"佢就係玩過覺得自己有織布就打得贏野豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be5d4d160650ef6f4ff134e86178a9b9764b02c","tid":1026701,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6398d1ff90450c5d602a78583845c51c721b34","tid":1026701,"uid":47374,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T10:05:59.000Z","msg":"以前要7個成年人拎晒弓箭先搞掂到一隻野豬<br />\n仲要間唔中死1個，乜而家啲人咁勇敢"},"citedBy":0,"r